OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union has today
OL,7,Fpublicly announced its preference to
OL,8,Freduce the number of professional
OL,9,Fclubs in Wales from four to two.
OL,11,FA formal consultation process will
OL,12,Fbegin on September 1 and last for four
OL,13,Fweeks. Recommendations will then be
OL,14,Fmade to the WRU Board, which will make
OL,15,Fthe final decision on a way forward by
OL,16,Fthe end of October.
