OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThere are four options put forward in
OL,7,Fthe proposals document from the WRU's
OL,8,FExecutive, led by chief executive Abi
OL,9,FTierney, with heavy input from new
OL,10,Fdirector of rugby Dave Reddin.
OL,12,FThe four options are:
OL,14,FIn the proposal document, the WRU
OL,15,Fproposes "radical and systemic change"
OL,16,Fand advances their case for proceeding
OL,17,Fwith Model D.
