OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThe majority of the document, which is
OL,7,F90 slides long, focuses on proceeding
OL,8,Fwith just two clubs but crucially it
OL,9,Fdoes not say which clubs would face
OL,10,Fthe axe.
OL,12,FThe Union's preference is to proceed
OL,13,Fwith two clubs, each housing a men's
OL,14,Fand women's professional side.
OL,16,FCardiff, Dragons, Ospreys and Scarlets
OL,17,Fhave been the four pro clubs in Wales
OL,18,Fsince the inception of regional rugby
OL,19,Fin 2003.
