OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThere has been no clarification yet on
OL,7,Fwhether the two clubs which go forward
OL,8,Fwould be existing entities or
OL,9,Fcompletely new teams.
OL,11,FWRU CEO Abi Tierney said: "We are
OL,12,Fclear that the current model in Wales
OL,13,Fis no longer delivering what our game
OL,14,Fneeds. This consultation is about
OL,15,Flistening. No decisions have been made
OL,16,Fand it's crucial that we work
OL,17,Ftogether."
