OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FWRU director of rugby Dave Reddin
OL,7,Fadded: "The approach we have designed
OL,8,Fis respectful, thorough, and inclusive
OL,9,Fand we encourage people to challenge
OL,10,Four ideas and help us create something
OL,11,Fthat we can all get behind."
OL,13,FThe WRU would fund all rugby
OL,14,Foperations, which would include
OL,15,Fcentrally contracting players.
OL,17,FPrivate investors would still retain
OL,18,Fownership of the clubs and be
OL,19,Fresponsible for their commercial
OL,20,Fperformance.
