OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThe men's teams at both clubs would
OL,7,Fhave a squad budget of #7.8million. In
OL,8,FEngland, there is a salary cap of
OL,9,F#7.8m with room for a "marquee player"
OL,10,Fto sit outside of that. In France, the
OL,11,Fsalary cap is #9.2m.
OL,13,FClubs would focus their resources on
OL,14,Fincreasing opportunities for Wales-
OL,15,Fqualified players, with a reduction to
OL,16,Fjust two players who are not qualified
OL,17,Fto represent Wales per club.
