OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FA cornerstone of the preferred option
OL,7,Fis the development of a new "national
OL,8,Fcampus" which would house both clubs
OL,9,Fand the national sides and academies.
OL,11,FThis would include shared strength and
OL,12,Fconditioning facilities, shared
OL,13,Fmedical and recovery facilities and
OL,14,Fshared catering.
OL,16,FThe idea behind it is to reduce
OL,17,Foverheads on things like medical
OL,18,Fsupplies, while encouraging the kind
OL,19,Fof collaboration which Reddin believes
OL,20,FWales needs to become a success.
