OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThere is no detail in the document
OL,7,Fregarding how much this would cost or
OL,8,Fhow long it would take to develop.
OL,10,FIn making the case for change, the WRU
OL,11,Fpoints out that the performance of the
OL,12,Fmen's and women's teams at
OL,13,Finternational and domestic level has
OL,14,Fbeen poor.
OL,16,FThey say clubs are not currently
OL,17,Ffunded to a level where they can be
OL,18,Fcompetitive and that significant
OL,19,Finvestment is required in facilities
OL,20,Fand coaching.
