OL,3,CWRU unveils radical proposal to halve
OL,4,Cnumber of pro rugby clubs in Wales
OL,6,FThe Union also believe that the top-
OL,7,Fend playing talent in Wales is too
OL,8,Fspread out and that key players don't
OL,9,Fplay enough rugby together, saying:
OL,10,F"It is clear that we have collectively
OL,11,Ffailed to collaborate."
OL,13,FIn the coming weeks, the Union will
OL,14,Fnow seek the opinions of key
OL,15,Fstakeholders, including clubs, players
OL,16,Fand sponsors.
OL,18,FThey insist that they are open to
OL,19,Fhearing alternative suggestions but
OL,20,Ftheir vision for Welsh rugby has now
OL,21,Fbeen made clear.
